movie, "The Secret,"

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:27.870 align:middle line:84%
and how it talks all about
the law of attraction.

00:00:27.870 --> 00:00:31.130 align:middle line:84%
Well, what about the
law of no matter what?

00:00:31.130 --> 00:00:33.600 align:middle line:84%
Lisa Nichols is one of
the visionary teachers

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:36.740 align:middle line:84%
of "The Secret," and she is
here to keep it absolutely

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:39.730 align:middle line:84%
