It was confined.

00:08:24.120 --> 00:08:25.100 align:middle line:90%
It was judgmental.

00:08:25.100 --> 00:08:25.910 align:middle line:90%
It was painful.

00:08:25.910 --> 00:08:26.920 align:middle line:90%
It was hurtful.

