>>LISA: Church dress.

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:56.991 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: Exactly.

00:08:56.991 --> 00:08:58.580 align:middle line:90%
I would not be allowed there.

00:08:58.580 --> 00:09:00.780 align:middle line:90%
And so I was just interested.

00:09:00.780 --> 00:09:06.650 align:middle line:84%
