saying I want to use you.

00:09:06.650 --> 00:09:07.990 align:middle line:90%
Like I could hear your voice.

00:09:07.990 --> 00:09:09.560 align:middle line:84%
I had never heard
God as a child,

00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:13.000 align:middle line:84%
