I want to use you.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:15.512 align:middle line:84%
I need you-- I
kid you not, Lisa.

00:09:15.512 --> 00:09:16.720 align:middle line:90%
This is exactly what he said.

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:19.430 align:middle line:84%
I need you to go
heal my children.

00:09:19.430 --> 00:09:22.650 align:middle line:84%
So I began to work
with kids, teenagers.

00:09:22.650 --> 00:09:23.910 align:middle line:90%
