>>LISA: Why isn't
it any different?

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:16.420 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, I wanted it.

00:16:16.420 --> 00:16:18.044 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: How did
I end up here again?

00:16:18.044 --> 00:16:19.300 align:middle line:90%
No, this was a new place.

00:16:19.300 --> 00:16:20.906 align:middle line:84%
You just brought
old habits to it.

00:16:20.906 --> 00:16:21.600 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh.

00:16:21.600 --> 00:16:23.420 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: Right,
it's kind of sobering.

00:16:23.420 --> 00:16:23.920 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:16:23.920 --> 00:16:24.961 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: It's sobering.

00:16:24.961 --> 00:16:26.370 align:middle line:90%
It's very sobering.

00:16:26.370 --> 00:16:28.745 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: The question I've been
asking myself a lot lately

00:16:28.745 --> 00:16:31.680 align:middle line:84%
is how do you break
through to that next level

00:16:31.680 --> 00:16:35.120 align:middle line:84%
without having any reference
point and a ton of old habits?

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:35.800 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: Yes.

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:38.010 align:middle line:84%
So number one is the
part that most people

00:16:38.010 --> 00:16:40.400 align:middle line:84%
don't want to do because
I think it's called zero.

00:16:40.400 --> 00:16:44.350 align:middle line:84%
You have to stand in 100%
accountability and ownership

00:16:44.350 --> 00:16:45.750 align:middle line:90%
for your break down.

00:16:45.750 --> 00:16:47.900 align:middle line:84%
Everyone wants to fast-forward
to the breakthrough.

00:16:47.900 --> 00:16:51.100 align:middle line:84%
Listen, you can't Google
download your breakthrough.

00:16:51.100 --> 00:16:52.260 align:middle line:90%
Google is the Internet.

00:16:52.260 --> 00:16:53.860 align:middle line:90%
It was invented 20 years ago.

00:16:53.860 --> 00:16:55.340 align:middle line:84%
We've been living
for a long time.

00:16:55.340 --> 00:16:57.570 align:middle line:84%
You can't Google download
your breakthrough.

00:16:57.570 --> 00:17:00.929 align:middle line:84%
So first you have to
understand what's in breakdown.

00:17:00.929 --> 00:17:01.970 align:middle line:90%
We don't want to do that.

00:17:01.970 --> 00:17:04.150 align:middle line:84%
People come to me from all
over the world, my students.

00:17:04.150 --> 00:17:05.670 align:middle line:84%
And they go give
me a breakthrough.

00:17:05.670 --> 00:17:06.410 align:middle line:84%
You're the breakthrough
specialist.

00:17:06.410 --> 00:17:08.230 align:middle line:84%
I say OK, let's find
out what's in breakdown?

00:17:08.230 --> 00:17:09.510 align:middle line:84%
They're like no, I don't
want to talk about that.

00:17:09.510 --> 00:17:10.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:17:10.030 --> 00:17:10.990 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: Can you hurry up
and get me to a breakthrough.

00:17:10.990 --> 00:17:11.980 align:middle line:90%
I've only got three days.

00:17:11.980 --> 00:17:12.170 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:17:12.170 --> 00:17:13.060 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: I'm like hold on.

00:17:13.060 --> 00:17:14.230 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I want to
get to manifesting.

00:17:14.230 --> 00:17:15.010 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:17:15.010 --> 00:17:15.061 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: Right, exactly.

00:17:15.061 --> 00:17:15.364 align:middle line:90%
I want a manifest.

00:17:15.364 --> 00:17:16.180 align:middle line:90%
I want a vision.

00:17:16.180 --> 00:17:17.721 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to deal
with that stuff.

00:17:17.721 --> 00:17:20.240 align:middle line:84%
And in order to get
to a breakthrough,

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:24.660 align:middle line:84%
you have to be willing to really
unpack your breakdown so you

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:25.839 align:middle line:90%
can go to the source of it.

00:17:25.839 --> 00:17:28.470 align:middle line:84%
Now in order to
unpack it correctly,

00:17:28.470 --> 00:17:30.740 align:middle line:84%
you need to unpack it
in different categories.

00:17:30.740 --> 00:17:33.109 align:middle line:84%
I call it the nine
environments of you.

00:17:33.109 --> 00:17:35.400 align:middle line:84%
You need to unpack it in
different categories, not just

00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:36.450 align:middle line:90%
my life.

00:17:36.450 --> 00:17:38.045 align:middle line:90%
Unpack your spirituality.

00:17:38.045 --> 00:17:39.680 align:middle line:90%
What's in breakdown there?

00:17:39.680 --> 00:17:40.780 align:middle line:90%
Unpack your finances.

00:17:40.780 --> 00:17:41.970 align:middle line:90%
What's in breakdown there?

00:17:41.970 --> 00:17:43.060 align:middle line:90%
Unpack your relationship.

00:17:43.060 --> 00:17:46.500 align:middle line:84%
Love, family, friends,
each separately.

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:48.595 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That can
be overwhelming.

00:17:48.595 --> 00:17:49.220 align:middle line:90%
Just the three.

00:17:49.220 --> 00:17:50.350 align:middle line:90%
I mean, there's six more to go.

00:17:50.350 --> 00:17:50.564 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: Yeah.

00:17:50.564 --> 00:17:51.590 align:middle line:90%
There's six more to go.

00:17:51.590 --> 00:17:53.679 align:middle line:84%
And then to be OK,
don't get stuck--

00:17:53.679 --> 00:17:54.220 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:17:54.220 --> 00:17:54.600 align:middle line:90%
How do you not get--

00:17:54.600 --> 00:17:55.716 align:middle line:90%
--in the reality of now.

00:17:55.716 --> 00:17:57.340 align:middle line:84%
So number one, make
it black and white.

00:17:57.340 --> 00:17:58.506 align:middle line:90%
Don't just get in your head.

00:17:58.506 --> 00:18:00.849 align:middle line:84%
Get it out of your head
because emotions are there.

00:18:00.849 --> 00:18:02.890 align:middle line:84%
You mix between your head
and your heart so much.

00:18:02.890 --> 00:18:07.150 align:middle line:84%
So put it on paper, rate it from
a one to a five, one to a five.

00:18:07.150 --> 00:18:09.610 align:middle line:84%
Five is it's absolutely,
exactly like I want it,

00:18:09.610 --> 00:18:11.010 align:middle line:90%
and one being it's in breakdown.

00:18:11.010 --> 00:18:12.260 align:middle line:90%
It's in complete breakdown.

00:18:12.260 --> 00:18:13.100 align:middle line:90%
And so you rate it.

00:18:13.100 --> 00:18:14.410 align:middle line:84%
If it's a two, I
need to work on it.

00:18:14.410 --> 00:18:15.150 align:middle line:84%
If it's a one, I
need to work on it.

00:18:15.150 --> 00:18:16.240 align:middle line:84%
If it's a three, I
need to work on it.

00:18:16.240 --> 00:18:16.860 align:middle line:90%
Period.

00:18:16.860 --> 00:18:17.610 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's it.

00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:18.470 align:middle line:90%
You just get it out.

00:18:18.470 --> 00:18:18.580 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: Just rate it.

00:18:18.580 --> 00:18:19.780 align:middle line:90%
Just get it out and rate it.

00:18:19.780 --> 00:18:22.880 align:middle line:84%
And then just go focus on
your threes, twos, and ones.

00:18:22.880 --> 00:18:24.800 align:middle line:84%
And whatever is in a
one, go there first.

00:18:24.800 --> 00:18:25.970 align:middle line:90%
Don't try to do all of them.

00:18:25.970 --> 00:18:27.260 align:middle line:90%
You have a lifetime.

00:18:27.260 --> 00:18:28.220 align:middle line:90%
You have a lifetime.

00:18:28.220 --> 00:18:32.340 align:middle line:84%
I laser on one area every
45 days to a quarter.

00:18:32.340 --> 00:18:35.170 align:middle line:84%
If it's kind of big, and then
I give myself 90 days for it.

00:18:35.170 --> 00:18:38.314 align:middle line:84%
But one, penetrate deep and
narrow, deep and narrow.

00:18:38.314 --> 00:18:40.230 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And taking it
on all at once doesn't--

00:18:40.230 --> 00:18:41.880 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: It's what you
said, it's overwhelming.

00:18:41.880 --> 00:18:42.690 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --which is what I do.

00:18:42.690 --> 00:18:44.400 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: But that's
what super achievers do.

00:18:44.400 --> 00:18:45.910 align:middle line:84%
I want to clean it
all up right now.

00:18:45.910 --> 00:18:46.880 align:middle line:90%
Wait, wait, wait.

00:18:46.880 --> 00:18:48.555 align:middle line:90%
Clean it up one room at a time.

00:18:48.555 --> 00:18:50.110 align:middle line:90%
Clean up one corner at a time.

00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:53.580 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Are you in that over
achievers' anonymous category

00:18:53.580 --> 00:18:54.080 align:middle line:90%
or not?

00:18:54.080 --> 00:18:56.143 align:middle line:84%
I mean, have you broken
that habit in your life?

00:18:56.143 --> 00:18:56.726 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: No.

00:18:56.726 --> 00:18:57.610 align:middle line:90%
No, I haven't.

00:18:57.610 --> 00:18:58.354 align:middle line:90%
I manage it.

00:18:58.354 --> 00:18:59.270 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You manage it?

00:18:59.270 --> 00:19:00.470 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: I manage it.

00:19:00.470 --> 00:19:03.910 align:middle line:84%
I tell people I am
so far from perfect.

00:19:03.910 --> 00:19:06.335 align:middle line:84%
Only thing I do differently
is I manage my imperfection

00:19:06.335 --> 00:19:07.626 align:middle line:90%
a lot better than other people.

00:19:07.626 --> 00:19:08.167 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Whew.

00:19:08.167 --> 00:19:08.810 align:middle line:90%
Good, good.

00:19:08.810 --> 00:19:10.268 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: I'm so
far from perfect,

00:19:10.268 --> 00:19:12.390 align:middle line:84%
but I just know how to
manage my imperfection.

00:19:12.390 --> 00:19:13.245 align:middle line:90%
I've been with me.

00:19:13.245 --> 00:19:14.620 align:middle line:84%
You've been with
you a long time.

00:19:14.620 --> 00:19:14.940 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:19:14.940 --> 00:19:16.231 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: You know your stuff.

00:19:16.231 --> 00:19:19.130 align:middle line:84%
I tell people we're sneaky
because we're brilliant.

00:19:19.130 --> 00:19:21.970 align:middle line:84%
My excuses have Swarovski
crystals on them, honey.

00:19:21.970 --> 00:19:25.300 align:middle line:84%
I mean, my junk looks good,
so I have to watch out.

00:19:25.300 --> 00:19:28.190 align:middle line:84%
I have to hold myself
accountable at a higher level.

00:19:28.190 --> 00:19:30.390 align:middle line:84%
And so I know where
I have breakdown.

00:19:30.390 --> 00:19:32.450 align:middle line:90%
I know that I love to say yes.

00:19:32.450 --> 00:19:32.950 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:19:32.950 --> 00:19:34.158 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: I love to say yes.

00:19:34.158 --> 00:19:36.950 align:middle line:84%
So I ask the people around me
who are in my support circle,

00:19:36.950 --> 00:19:38.630 align:middle line:90%
help me to say no.

00:19:38.630 --> 00:19:41.270 align:middle line:84%
So I need you to
ask me this way.

00:19:41.270 --> 00:19:44.000 align:middle line:84%
So I actually enrolled the
support of my community.

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:44.500 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh.

00:19:44.500 --> 00:19:47.420 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: I need you to ask
me Lisa, can you make it here?

00:19:47.420 --> 00:19:49.830 align:middle line:84%
If you come, are you
not doing something else

00:19:49.830 --> 00:19:51.200 align:middle line:90%
you should be doing?

00:19:51.200 --> 00:19:53.807 align:middle line:90%
That answer normally is yes.

00:19:53.807 --> 00:19:54.640 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Interesting.

00:19:54.640 --> 00:19:55.760 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: I ask for help.

00:19:55.760 --> 00:19:58.810 align:middle line:84%
See, super achievers have a
tendency to not ask for help.

00:19:58.810 --> 00:20:01.500 align:middle line:84%
When you realize that the
cape on your back is not real,

00:20:01.500 --> 00:20:04.860 align:middle line:84%
honey, and the S on
your chest is Crayola,

00:20:04.860 --> 00:20:06.520 align:middle line:84%
you'll realize that
every night when

00:20:06.520 --> 00:20:08.490 align:middle line:84%
you get in the shower,
your S washes off,

00:20:08.490 --> 00:20:10.560 align:middle line:84%
and that superhero
conversation is not true.

00:20:10.560 --> 00:20:13.170 align:middle line:84%
That supershero
conversation is not true.

00:20:13.170 --> 00:20:15.540 align:middle line:84%
You're an ordinary
woman choosing every day

00:20:15.540 --> 00:20:17.570 align:middle line:90%
to make extraordinary decisions.

00:20:17.570 --> 00:20:19.510 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Oh, and my mind
becomes my kryptonite

00:20:19.510 --> 00:20:21.760 align:middle line:84%
where I start to negative
self-talk everything I

00:20:21.760 --> 00:20:22.344 align:middle line:90%
didn't do.

00:20:22.344 --> 00:20:23.760 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: And
then every time you

00:20:23.760 --> 00:20:26.210 align:middle line:84%
do that, you draw a little
bit of energy from yourself.

00:20:26.210 --> 00:20:28.350 align:middle line:84%
And a little bit of your
life seeps out of you.

00:20:28.350 --> 00:20:30.740 align:middle line:90%
See, here's what I learned.

00:20:30.740 --> 00:20:33.140 align:middle line:84%
I learned that
the world is going

00:20:33.140 --> 00:20:35.170 align:middle line:84%
to follow my example
of how I treat me.

00:20:35.170 --> 00:20:37.560 align:middle line:84%
The same thing that you
heard me say with Oprah.

00:20:37.560 --> 00:20:40.320 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't just say it
because it was a sexy cliche.

00:20:40.320 --> 00:20:42.190 align:middle line:84%
I realized that I was
teaching the world

00:20:42.190 --> 00:20:43.367 align:middle line:90%
that I didn't need rest.

00:20:43.367 --> 00:20:45.825 align:middle line:84%
I was teaching the world that
I didn't need acknowledgment.

00:20:45.825 --> 00:20:46.590 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:20:46.590 --> 00:20:48.131 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: I was
teaching the world--

00:20:48.131 --> 00:20:50.100 align:middle line:84%
you know how when you
say don't worry about me.

00:20:50.100 --> 00:20:51.105 align:middle line:90%
You go on.

00:20:51.105 --> 00:20:52.370 align:middle line:90%
Oh, no, no, you guys go.

00:20:52.370 --> 00:20:53.770 align:middle line:90%
I'll be fine.

00:20:53.770 --> 00:20:54.770 align:middle line:90%
No, I got this.

00:20:54.770 --> 00:20:55.396 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Uh-huh.

00:20:55.396 --> 00:20:56.728 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: You're teaching them.

00:20:56.728 --> 00:20:58.370 align:middle line:84%
You're training
your family, you're

00:20:58.370 --> 00:21:00.870 align:middle line:84%
training your friends
that she has it.

00:21:00.870 --> 00:21:01.810 align:middle line:90%
She's perfect.

00:21:01.810 --> 00:21:03.060 align:middle line:90%
She's got it all covered.

00:21:03.060 --> 00:21:04.890 align:middle line:84%
And then, all of a
sudden, you feel lonely.

00:21:04.890 --> 00:21:06.565 align:middle line:84%
And no one's coming
to lift your arms up

00:21:06.565 --> 00:21:07.565 align:middle line:90%
when they get too heavy.

00:21:07.565 --> 00:21:08.040 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You're breaking down.

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:09.800 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: Well, that's
because you've been doing this

00:21:09.800 --> 00:21:11.470 align:middle line:84%
all the time, lifting
their arms up,

00:21:11.470 --> 00:21:14.840 align:middle line:84%
they've never even seen you in
a moment of saying I need rest.

00:21:14.840 --> 00:21:16.870 align:middle line:84%
The best give I gave
to myself, Lisa,

00:21:16.870 --> 00:21:18.750 align:middle line:90%
was declaring to my community.

00:21:18.750 --> 00:21:19.790 align:middle line:90%
I need rest.

00:21:19.790 --> 00:21:20.747 align:middle line:90%
I went to my son.

00:21:20.747 --> 00:21:21.830 align:middle line:90%
You might want to do this.

00:21:21.830 --> 00:21:22.680 align:middle line:90%
I went to my son.

00:21:22.680 --> 00:21:24.346 align:middle line:84%
I think I may have
told you this before.

00:21:24.346 --> 00:21:25.210 align:middle line:90%
I did.

00:21:25.210 --> 00:21:26.430 align:middle line:90%
I told you this.

00:21:26.430 --> 00:21:27.314 align:middle line:90%
I told you this.

00:21:27.314 --> 00:21:28.198 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes, you did.

00:21:28.198 --> 00:21:30.170 align:middle line:90%
Yes, you did.

00:21:30.170 --> 00:21:34.090 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: Go to your family
and say I owe you an apology.

00:21:34.090 --> 00:21:36.152 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:21:36.152 --> 00:21:38.110 align:middle line:84%
Can't tell you how many
times I have done this.

00:21:38.110 --> 00:21:38.834 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:21:38.834 --> 00:21:41.000 align:middle line:84%
>>NICHOLS: Didn't things
begin to immediately shift?

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:42.500 align:middle line:84%
Because they have
compassion for you.

00:21:42.500 --> 00:21:43.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:44.350 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: I owe you an apology.

00:21:44.350 --> 00:21:45.770 align:middle line:90%
I'm so sorry.

00:21:45.770 --> 00:21:48.429 align:middle line:84%
I made you think
that I was perfect.

00:21:48.429 --> 00:21:49.470 align:middle line:90%
Can I look right at them?

00:21:49.470 --> 00:21:49.970 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:21:49.970 --> 00:21:50.597 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:21:50.597 --> 00:21:51.930 align:middle line:90%
>>NICHOLS: This is what you say.

00:21:51.930 --> 00:21:53.310 align:middle line:90%
I owe you an apology.

00:21:53.310 --> 00:21:55.840 align:middle line:84%
I made you think that
I don't need rest.

00:21:55.840 --> 00:21:58.590 align:middle line:84%
I made you think that
I don't need help.

00:21:58.590 --> 00:22:01.370 align:middle line:84%
I made you think that I
don't need to hear thank you,

00:22:01.370 --> 00:22:05.130 align:middle line:84%
and I love you, I'm sorry,
I'm grateful for you.

00:22:05.130 --> 00:22:06.780 align:middle line:90%
I apologize.

00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:10.100 align:middle line:84%
I made you think I was a
supershero or a superhero.

00:22:10.100 --> 00:22:12.790 align:middle line:90%
I realize I'm human.

00:22:12.790 --> 00:22:14.220 align:middle line:90%
And I need rest.

00:22:14.220 --> 00:22:18.290 align:middle line:84%
I made you think that I love
cooking five days a week.

00:22:18.290 --> 00:22:19.900 align:middle line:90%
I apologize.

00:22:19.900 --> 00:22:24.180 align:middle line:84%
I love making reservations
sometimes, too.

00:22:24.180 --> 00:22:27.162 align:middle line:84%
Just surrender
inside the realness.

00:22:27.162 --> 00:22:28.870 align:middle line:84%
That's a level of
realness with yourself.

00:22:28.870 --> 00:22:30.850 align:middle line:84%
But you've got to be
comfortable seeing

00:22:30.850 --> 00:22:32.590 align:middle line:90%
that much of realness from you.

00:22:32.590 --> 00:22:35.200 align:middle line:84%
See, you're not
protecting the ordinary,

00:22:35.200 --> 00:22:36.852 align:middle line:90%
the woman from the world, Lisa.

00:22:36.852 --> 00:22:38.560 align:middle line:84%
You're protecting the
woman from yourself

00:22:38.560 --> 00:22:40.310 align:middle line:84%
because you don't
quite know-- well,

00:22:40.310 --> 00:22:42.000 align:middle line:84%
