>>NICHOLS: We share it, and I
want you to know that as I hope

00:58:09.130 --> 00:58:09.960 align:middle line:90%
I'm a gift to you--

00:58:09.960 --> 00:58:10.501 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

